data.description: Jackson Run North brings LENNAR''s signature suite of Everything''s Included extras & upgrades to Whitestown, IN. Residents will enjoy amenities including walking trails, 2 ponds & a community center w/a pool, pool house, playground & basketball court.  Easy access to I-65 & downtown Indy. The first level of the Hampshire offers a 5th bedroom/flex room as an ideal space for overnight stays. The Great Room, kitchen & dining room can also be found on the first floor, arranged in an expansive floorplan. Donat miss the light filled morning room! Upstairs, four bedrooms await, plus a loft offering additional living space for everyone. A 3 car garage adds extra storage. *Photos/Tour of model may show features not selected in home.
